00:07:58.100 --> 00:07:59.860
Gomu gomu no

00:08:00.860 --> 00:08:02.200
diable jambe

00:08:02.660 --> 00:08:03.480
crosse

00:08:06.420 --> 00:08:07.970
elephant gun

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:10.050
strike

